Description: Everyone needs a place to lay their weary head. For travelers visiting Ho Chi Minh City, Ngoc Yen Hotel is an excellent choice for rest and rejuvenation. Well-known for its proximity to great restaurants, Ngoc Yen Hotel makes it easy to enjoy the best of Ho Chi Minh City. Rooms at Ngoc Yen Hotel provide air conditioning, and guests can stay connected with free wifi. In addition, while staying at Ngoc Yen Hotel guests have access to a 24 hour front desk, room service, and baggage storage. Need a place to park? Free parking is available at Ngoc Yen Hotel. While staying at Ngoc Yen Hotel, visitors can check out Pham Ngu Lao Street (1.5 mi) and Bui Vien Street (1.6 mi), some of Ho Chi Minh City's top attractions. While you’re here, be sure to check out some of the southwestern restaurants, including TnT BBQ, La Fiesta, and Tippy's, all of which are a short distance from Ngoc Yen Hotel. If you’re looking for something to do, Couleurs by Rehahn Fine Art Photography, Artinus 3D Art Museum, and Aitch Space are a nice way to spend some time. Ngoc Yen Hotel is sure to make your visit to Ho Chi Minh City one worth remembering.
